"Where Do We Go From Here?" audiobook reading of a Philip Agee article from the book "Dirty Work: The CIA in Western Europe". Philip Agee discusses and criticizes the intelligence investigations of the 1970s, including the Rockefeller Commission, the Church Committee, the Pike Committee and more. A full copy of the book can be found here: https://archive.org/details/pdfy-9MwmH_nnJ4eOmL66 and its companion volume, "Dirty Work 2: The CIA in Africa" can be found here: https://archive.org/details/CIAInAfrica

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub